text: Takashi Kondo (29 October 1911 - 23 January 1994) was a Japanese gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1932 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:1994 deaths Category:Japanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Gymnasts at the 1932 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tokyo
